reporting-org.narrative: New Zealand Ministry of Foreign Affairs and Trade

description.narrative: Co-funding with a PNG lead firm to expand its fresh produce business by developing depots, a cool store and extension services to farmers. This will enable three villages to increase production from 15 tonnes of produce (prior to MFATs co-investment) to 80 tonnes per month while growing their supplier base from 500 farmers to over 2500.
